{"id":188849,"type":2,"name":"ハゼドン","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/0e/96/188849_Rdf84.jpg","summary":"決してカッコイイとはいえないハゼの子であるハゼドン（小学3年生の男の子という設定[1]）は、母が死に際に言い残した「世界一強い魚になって、南の国へ行くんだよ」との約束を果たすため、人魚のシーランとフグのプーヤンと一緒に冒険の旅に出る。\r\n形見の貝殻のペンダントは、ハゼドンが世界一強い魚になったときに開くことになっているが、中にどんな秘密が隠されているかは誰も知らない。\r\nハゼドンは擬人化されており、尾びれで歩く描写がある。その一方で他の魚が泳ぐ描写もある[1]。海の中が舞台ではあるが、川が流れている場面もみられる。","info":"<li><span>话数: </span>26</li><li><span>放送开始: </span>1972-10-5</li><li><span>放送星期: </span>26</li><li><span>导演: </span><a href=\"/person/1513\" rel=\"v:directedBy\">出﨑統</a>、<a href=\"/person/2643\" rel=\"v:directedBy\">池野文雄</a></li><li><span>分镜: </span><a href=\"/person/1513\">出﨑統</a>、<a href=\"/person/2643\">池野文雄</a>、<a href=\"/person/1684\">出崎哲</a>、<a href=\"/person/613\">富野由悠季</a></li><li><span>原画: </span><a href=\"/person/2482\">河島治之</a></li><li><span>背景美术: </span><a href=\"/person/11891\">スタジオじゃっく</a></li><li><span>播放结束: </span>1973-3-29</li>","collection":{"wish":4,"collect":1,"doing":1,"on_hold":2,"dropped":2},"tags":[{"name":"TV","count":2},{"name":"1972年10月","count":1},{"name":"赛璐珞","count":1},{"name":"1972年十月番","count":1},{"name":"70s","count":1},{"name":"1972","count":1},{"name":"1972年","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":652901,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/652901","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":652902,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/652902","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":652903,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/652903","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":652904,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/652904","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":652905,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/652905","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":652906,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/652